metadata.name: Parallel Worlds #1
metadata.description:
Which one is the world we live in?

A story about parallel worlds reflecting above the sky of somewhere in Japan, there are sun and moon appearing on the same time. 

We can live a normal life on both world, but the myth can be happened on either world too. The world that all seasons come together. The world that human are not seen. The world that only architecture and nature live.
